docs.text: Welcome to Middle Earth Folk Three rings for the Elven Kings, under the sky. Seven for the Dwarf Lords, in their halls of stone. Of Elves Elves are from the West, and will return to the West at the end of the Third Age. Of Men Men are mortal, and are thus sometimes greedy and suspect. Approach with caution.
